/// Deserializes a string into a type.
/// 
/// This function will attempt to interpret `s` as a TOML document and
/// deserialize `T` from the document.
/// 
/// To deserializes TOML values, instead of documents, see [`ValueDeserializer`].
/// 
/// # Examples
